item.g:description: HighlightsPersonalise your Home Screen. Tint your icons with any colour. Rearrange and resize apps and widgets. With on-device processing and Private Cloud Compute, no one but you can access your data — not even Apple. It stores them securely and syncs across your devices with end-to-end encryption. You can also control which contacts to share with an app, rather than giving it access to all your contacts. And you can choose to share more contacts over time.
